    "created_at": "2025-08-15T12:12:38Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-08-15T12:15:08Z",
    "body": "This is not fixed as of 1.23.0.\n\n\n```toml\nformat = \"\"\"$shell $character\"\"\"\n\n[shell]\ndisabled = false\nformat = '([$indicator]($style) )'\nfish_indicator = ''\n```\n\n```shell\n❯ # in fish\n❯ bash\n❯ # in bash\n```\n\nRemoving format:\n\n```shell\n  ❯ # in fish\n  ❯ bash\nbsh  ❯ # in bash\n```\n\n```shell\n❯ starship --version\nstarship 1.23.0\nbranch:\ncommit_hash:\nbuild_time:2025-04-27 15:52:14 +00:00\nbuild_env:rustc 1.86.0 (05f9846f8 2025-03-31) (Homebrew),\n```",
